strings: <voice_0x01000F46><se_low>*: It depicts the heart of the Argonauts in Prince Charles' hand.
<voice_0x01000F48><se_high>*: I've never seen such a huge argan heart!
<voice_0x01000F49><se_high>*: This will be the biggest launch ever!
<voice_0x01000F4A><se_def>*: He must destroy all Argan Lizards to win heart and mind.
<voice_0x01000F4B><se_low>*: Prince Charles! Dedicated to King Clavius, the heart of the Argonne, a symbol of his courage and dignity!
<voice_0x01000F4D><se_low>the key: Can you swear to god you got an argan heart from a dead argan lizard?
<voice_0x01000F4E><se_def>the prince carlos: Well... Dad of course!
<voice_0x01000F4F><se_low>the key: Even if you and others are helping him to fight. I still remember his claim to the throne.
<voice_0x01000F50><se_low>the key: However, the throne cannot be verified through any other means of acquisition. You are doing well.
<voice_0x01000F51><se_def>the prince carlos: What! everything is fine! I have a chameleon in my hand. It's a terrible animal!
<voice_0x01000F52><se_low>the key: I salute you. Take this heart of Arjuna as a test of his true identity.
